verbose_text: Unexpectedly, Raptor deficiency had no significant effect on differentiation (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), basal and beta3-adrenegic signaling induced UCP1, as well as the expression of PPARgamma and adiponectin (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), or O 2 consumption (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY) in primary differentiated adipocytes from iWAT and BAT.
